headline: PNC Announces Redemption of 4.758% Fixed Rate/Floating Rate Senior Notes Due Jan. 26, 2027
summary: The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc. (NYSE: PNC) today announced the redemption of, on Jan. 26, 2026, all outstanding 4.758% Fixed Rate/Floating Rate Senior Notes due Jan. 26, 2027, issued by PNC in the amount of $1,250,000,000 (CUSIP 693475 BL8). The securities have an original scheduled maturity date of Jan. 26, 2027.
